M|subagent-driven-development|Execute plan by dispatching fresh subagent per task, with two-stage rv after each: spec compliance rv first, then code quality rv.
M|subagent-driven-development|**Why subagents:** You delegate tasks to specialized agents with isolated ctx. By precisely crafting their instructions and ctx, you ensure they stay focused and succeed at their task. They should nev
M|subagent-driven-development|**Core principle:** Fresh subagent per task + two-stage rv (spec then quality) = high quality, fast iteration
