M|subagent-driven-development|**vs. Executing Plans (parallel ses):**
M|subagent-driven-development|- Same ses (no ctx switch)
M|subagent-driven-development|- Fresh subagent per task (no ctx pollution)
M|subagent-driven-development|- Two-stage rv after each task: spec compliance first, then code quality
M|subagent-driven-development|- Faster iteration (no human-in-loop between tasks)
